        <para id="id2258754">ane <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:msubsup><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msubsup><m:msub><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msub></m:mrow></m:math>. This recursively generates square submatrices
of <m:math><m:mi>H</m:mi></m:math> similar to those defined in <link target-id="uid9"/> and <link target-id="uid11"/> and shows the
basic structure of the dynamic system.</para>
